{
  "texts": [
    "All scenarios used the same q value of 0.5 21 when finding the \"less likely\" predictions.",
    "Extra data cleaning steps were needed before the UN Comtrade data was able to be transformed into a supply network of shipping goods between countries.",
    "Several steps recommended in 38 were used to limit the effects of outliers, missing data, and mismatched bilateral trade records.",
    "First, unit price was calculated from the value and quantity variables captured for each transaction record.",
    "A conservative upper percentile cut of 99% was used to identify and to remove only the most extreme outliers."
  ]
}